               <head>Miscellaneous Sufi works</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Collection of four Sufi works. Not dated. Detached binding; tooled medalions and bands; fragile. </summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008112367 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_956-item1">
                     <locus from="1v" to="88">ff. 1v-88</locus>
                     <note>
                        <p>Anonymous exposition detailing the doctrines and technicalities of Sufism. </p>
                        <p>The work is divided into thirty-four sections called uṣūl. </p>
                        <p>Not dated. </p>
                        <p>Painted sar'lawḥ. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21797">Uṣūl-i ḥāfiẓīyah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21797">اصول حافظيّه</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008112367 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807" n="2" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_956-item2">
                     <locus from="91" to="111">ff. 91-111</locus>
                     <note>
                        <p>Untitled work on the nature of God. </p>
                        <p>Not dated. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian </textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008112367 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807" n="3" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_956-item3">
                     <locus from="115" to="179">ff. 115-179</locus>
                     <note>
                        <p>Anonymous Sufi tract on divine unity or tawḥīd and related themes. </p>
                        <p>Not dated. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian </textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21798">Khazānat al-asrār</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21798">خزانة الاسرار</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008112367 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807" n="4" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_956-item4">
